{"word":"ὑπερόπτης","slug":"ὑπερόπτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερόπτης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὑπερόψομαι</el>\n<p/><i>a contemner, disdainer of</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>disdainful, haughty</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/>"}]}